    "description": "这个美丽的幻想世界永远不会对你有好感。 游戏模仿现实生活的许多方面。 在这个有魔法和怪物存在的世界里，你是微不足道的F佣兵。<br><br>选手们应该通过各种游戏信息不断思考如何生存下去。 饥饿、脱水、温度、月租、怪物威胁等 世界的环境总是威胁着你的生存。<br><br>另外，在伟大的旅程中，你会面临很多选择的十字路口。<br>你可能从不道德的决定中获益，也可能因为正确的决定而陷入危机。 你的选择会影响蝴蝶效应等伟大旅程的结束。<br><br>F级英雄故事在&quot;受控世界&quot;中追求金钱的政治火箭筒。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768270/extras/9219dd97b5c6b5dd413eac0fb130c5af.poster.avif?t=1646856607\" width=796 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768270/extras/9219dd97b5c6b5dd413eac0fb130c5af.webm?t=1646856607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768270/extras/9219dd97b5c6b5dd413eac0fb130c5af.mp4?t=1646856607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768270/extras/f822b0063283b0a98fb9ee274d983f99.poster.avif?t=1646856607\" width=592 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768270/extras/f822b0063283b0a98fb9ee274d983f99.webm?t=1646856607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768270/extras/f822b0063283b0a98fb9ee274d983f99.mp4?t=1646856607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>虽然不是只抓住怪物成为英雄的故事，但是为了增加资本，作为成功的雇佣兵，有必要战略性地利用资金<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >实时动作战</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768270/extras/3de4b7739f0b891cce6d15059dbbc7c5.poster.avif?t=1646856607\" width=390 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768270/extras/3de4b7739f0b891cce6d1