/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768270/extras/622dd1ea7f8cd50f6c58dbbd87d903a9.webm?t=1646856607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768270/extras/622dd1ea7f8cd50f6c58dbbd87d903a9.mp4?t=1646856607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在迷宫中寻找宝藏和珍品。 黄金伴随着风险。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深奥秘<br><br>加入从可怜的弗兰克佣兵到伟大英雄的伟大旅程吧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >各种项目</h2><br>医疗用品、药水、食品、武器、饰品、盔甲、杂货等400多种装备。<br><br>谜团与秘密</h2><br>解开各种谜题和世界秘密。",
